How about this.<br>
<br>
A guy living on a planet in another star system (lets just call him Duo) is sent away to a galactic prison. Before he leaves, his family gives him a magical stone, a stone that glows as long as the family is well.<br>
<br>
After a couple months in prison, Duo learns that a devestating plague has engulfed his home planet. The plague is so bad that the galactic government has decided to create a blockade of anything going into, or comming out of the plantet. Duo worries for his family, but is comforted by the fact that the magical stone is still glowing.<br>
<br>
Duo then decides that he must help his family, and to do so he must escape from prison, break through the blockade created around the planet and find his family before they are infected.<br>
<br>
OK, that's it. Please critique me, you can tell me if it sucks.<br>
<br>
I need a title.<br>
<br>
Somebody give me a better name that Duo, its to Gundam Wingy.<br>
<br>
I was also thinking that maybe the virus that has infected the planet creates anyone infected into demons. Or would that be too unoriginal?<br>
<br>
